    Separation of Concerns:

        Request DTOs for input validation

        Response DTOs for API output

        Simple DTOs for nested relationships

    Validation:

        Annotations like @NotBlank, @Email, @Pattern on request DTOs

        Proper field constraints matching entity validation

    Immutable Records:

        Using Java records for immutable DTOs

        Better thread safety and clarity

    Nested Relationships:

        Simple DTOs prevent circular references

        Avoid exposing unnecessary entity details

    Pagination Support:

        Can be added with Page<StudentResponseDTO> in controller responses